UICON Overview

Status Legend

full
The Pokemon is represented correctly and no fallback was needed

 fallback
When the icon represents the correct Pokemon, but fallback was used. (e.g. you want to display Purified Pikachu but the icon of normal Pikachu is used)

 overlay
When the base Mon is the same, but an overlay (like a costume) is missing. (e.g. you want to display Party hat Bulbasaur but the icon of normal Bulbasaur is used)
Warning: This is faulty for some Pokemon like FALL_2018 Pichu, 1st-form Spinda, trash-form Wormadam, standard Darmanitan and Galar evolutions like Obstagoon, Perrserker, Sirfetch’d, Mr. Rime and Runerigus

 missing
The Pokemon icon is missing and the default 0 icon is displayed
